1.0.name: wordpress/content-switcher
1.0.description:
Content Switcher allows you to easily insert into posts, pages and widgets of your website random numbers, and random or variable contents. You can use it, for example, to display COOKIE, ENV, GET, GLOBALS, POST, REQUEST, SERVER or SESSION variables. Content Switcher also allows you to optimize your website with Google Optimizer and to add the Google Analytics code to each page of your website.

  • Documentation
